(3, 2, 'Needs Improvement', 3, 'Interview completed. Score: 3/100 — Needs Improvement. Topics covered: Primary Role Skills, Secondary Skills.', '2026-03-14 05:35:47', 10, NULL),
(4, 2, 'Needs Improvement', 0, 'The candidate displayed a high degree of professional courtesy and punctuality throughout the session, which were the only areas where they showed any relative strength. Unfortunately, they failed to demonstrate even basic proficiency in coding, system design, or problem-solving, resulting in a complete inability to address the primary technical requirements of the role. This fundamental lack of software engineering knowledge and practical skill makes them an unsuitable candidate for this position.', '2026-03-14 05:38:39', 10, NULL),
(5, 2, 'Needs Improvement', 0, 'The candidate maintained a professional and communicative presence throughout the session, demonstrating an ability to engage politely with the interview team. However, they were unable to provide correct solutions or technical insights for any of the primary or secondary skill assessments required for a Software Engineering position. Their primary weakness was an absolute lack of foundational coding and problem-solving abilities, which prevented them from meeting any of the technical benchmarks for the role.', '2026-03-14 07:21:40', 10, NULL),
(6, 2, 'Needs Improvement', 8, 'Interview completed. Score: 8/100 — Needs Improvement. Topics covered: Primary Skills, Secondary Skills.', '2026-03-14 07:35:12', 10, NULL),
