(153, 16, 'Can you explain the concept of continuous integration and continuous deployment (CI/CD), and how do you use GitHub Actions to automate your workflow?', 'a', 'Secondary skills', 0, '[\"Good effort.\"]', '[\"Lack of understanding of CI/CD concepts\", \"Inability to provide a clear explanation\", \"Failure to mention GitHub Actions or automation workflow\"]', '[\"Research and study CI/CD pipelines and their importance in software development\", \"Familiarize yourself with GitHub Actions and its application in automating workflows\", \"Practice explaining technical concepts clearly and concisely\"]'),
