(157, 17, 'How do you optimize the performance of a MySQL database in a PHP application, and what are some common indexing strategies you use?', 'a', 'Primary role skills', 0, '[\"Good effort.\"]', '[\"Lack of understanding of MySQL optimization techniques\", \"Failure to provide common indexing strategies\", \"Inability to provide a clear and concise answer\"]', '[\"Study MySQL optimization techniques such as query optimization, indexing, and caching\", \"Research common indexing strategies such as B-tree indexing and hash indexing\", \"Practice providing clear and concise answers to technical questions\"]'),
