(175, 19, 'Can you explain the difference between MVC and MVVM architectural patterns and provide an example of when you would use each?', 'now o would ise', 'Primary role skills', 0, '[\"Good effort.\"]', '[\"Provide a clear and concise explanation of the difference between MVC and MVVM architectural patterns\", \"Offer relevant examples of when to use each pattern\", \"Demonstrate a basic understanding of iOS application development principles\"]', '[\"Study the Model-View-Controller (MVC) pattern and its application in iOS development\", \"Research the Model-View-ViewModel (MVVM) pattern and its benefits in separating concerns\", \"Practice explaining technical concepts in a clear and structured manner to improve communication skills\"]'),
(176, 19, 'How do you handle data binding in MVVM, and what are some common pitfalls to avoid?', 'mvm', 'Primary role skills', 0, '[\"Good effort.\"]', '[\"Lack of understanding of MVVM architecture\", \"Inability to explain data binding\", \"Failure to identify common pitfalls\"]', '[\"Study the MVVM architecture and its application in iOS development\", \"Learn about data binding techniques such as SwiftUI\'s @Published and @ObservableObject\", \"Research common pitfalls in MVVM implementation, such as overusing view models or not handling errors properly\"]'),
(177, 19, 'How would you design a modular architecture for a large-scale e-commerce application using PHP and MySQL?', 'ok', 'Primary role skills', 0, '[\"Good effort.\"]', '[\"Lack of relevant technical knowledge\", \"Failure to provide a clear design approach\", \"Inability to communicate technical ideas effectively\"]', '[\"Study and learn about modular architecture design patterns\", \"Research and practice designing large-scale e-commerce applications using PHP and MySQL\", \"Develop strong communication skills to effectively explain technical concepts and designs\"]'),
(178, 19, 'How do you ensure loose coupling between modules, and what strategies do you use for dependency management?', 'then', 'Primary role skills', 0, '[\"Good effort.\"]', '[\"Provide a clear and concise answer\", \"Explain the concept of loose coupling and its importance in iOS application development\", \"Discuss strategies for dependency management, such as using dependency injection or a dependency manager like CocoaPods or Swift Package Manager\"]', '[\"Study the Single Responsibility Principle and the Dependency Inversion Principle to understand how to achieve loose coupling\", \"Research and practice using dependency management tools like CocoaPods or Swift Package Manager\", \"Review iOS application architecture patterns, such as MVC, MVP, or MVVM, to understand how to separate concerns and reduce coupling between modules\"]'),
