(402, 43, 'How do you handle memory leaks in an Android application, and what tools or techniques do you use to detect them?\nFollow-up: Can you explain a scenario where you had to optimize the memory usage of an Android app, and what specific steps you took to resolve the issue?', 'dasdas', 'Image Processing', 3, '[\"Addressed the core concept of the Image Processing question.\", \"Provided a structured response.\"]', '[\"Consider adding more real-world examples.\", \"Expand on edge cases related to the topic.\"]', '[\"Review further documentation to improve confidence.\"]'),
